    "body": "Make sure you're reusing HTTP connections and not creating a new one for every request. If you make a new TCP connection for each request, and you concurrently do tons of requests, the OS will run out of sockets/file descriptors and will deny connecting.\r\n\r\nIt would help diagnose if you reported the error too. The empty JSON response probably also entails a socket level error that web3 is hiding.",
